And I say to you...

18:12.874 --> 18:14.136
[ grunts]

18:14.223 --> 18:16.486
Son of a [ bleep].

18:18.140 --> 18:19.446
If I'm elected...
[ bleep]

18:19.533 --> 18:21.839
the cafeteria's...
[ bleep]!

18:21.926 --> 18:24.190
And I promise to

18:24.277 --> 18:28.150
[ bleep]

