18:29.673 --> 18:32.720
Charge a man with a...
[ bleep].

18:32.807 --> 18:34.417
And... a victory

18:34.504 --> 18:37.507
for... [ bleep],
you big [ bleep].

18:37.594 --> 18:40.075
I promise to [ bleep] my

